profile: Riverbrink is the former retirement home of Samuel E. Weir, Q.C., (1898-1981) a collector of Canadian and International fine art, decorative artifacts, books and furniture.  Every year we display a portion of this permanent collection for the public to appreciate.  We really are one of Queenston's best kept little secrets!
